::Annihilator/Killer/Zeus::

Annihilator ducks, the shots going over his head and hitting a panel behind 
him, which quickly falls on his head.

Annihilator stumbles around the room, saying strange things, nearly crashing 
into Killer and Zeus, who are rushing in.

"Next time, leave a door or two open so we don't have to blast through a 
wall, idiot!" Killer yells, instantly opening fire on Megatron.

Zeus looks at Ra, surprised that he was frying the controll panel.

"Brother, are you allright?" Zeus asks Ra.

"He baked cookies with Megashron and'sh beshrayin' us," Annihilator says in a 
dazed tone, stumbling by. He was having trouble pronouncing letter due to the 
damage to his head.

Zeus looks at Ra, anger in his eyes as he holds his gun ready. "Is this true, 
brother?"
